data.description: DON'T MISS OUT!!Experience the epitome of Southern California living in this stunning single-family home located at 28338 Wellsville St, Murrieta, CA 92563. Nestled in a prime location, this residence offers not only a beautiful, open, and upgraded interior but also proximity to an array of conveniences, making it an ideal place to call home. As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the meticulous care and thoughtful design that has gone into this property. The low-maintenance lifestyle it offers is complemented by a plethora of amenities that make everyday living a breeze. The Homeowners Association (HOA) takes care of the front yard, allowing you to focus on enjoying your private back patio oasis complete with a luxurious spa. Embrace the sense of community as you explore the walking trails, take a dip in the pool, unwind in the spa, or simply enjoy the nearby park. With new shops and eateries within walking distance, you'll have the best of both worlds - a serene retreat and access to modern conveniences. Inside, the well-thought-out and flowing floorplan boasts upgraded flooring that adds a touch of elegance to every step. The lower level features a cozy den with a fireplace and a convenient half bath, perfect for entertaining or relaxing with loved ones. The open and highly functional kitchen has been thoughtfully upgraded with a new range and dishwasher, creating a space where culinary adventures come to life. It seamlessly opens to the family room, ensuring that you never miss a moment with family and friends while preparing meals. Venturing upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms. Two of these bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bathroom, providing comfort and convenience. The main suite is a true sanctuary with a walk-in closet, offering ample storage space for your personal belongings. it's a wonderful home that caters to your every need. Combine this with its fabulous location, and you have the perfect opportunity to experience the quintessential Southern California lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your new home. DON'T MISS OUT!!
